<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>This Minimum Equipment List (MEL) is an official manual published in English. It is approved by the Civil Aviation Authority of Vietnam (CAAV).</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>This MEL takes into account the specific configuration of each aircraft of VNA B787's fleet.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem rev:revStatus="R" rev:revHighlight="Update revision record">
<Para>This MEL REV 30SEP25  is based on and incorporates all changes in DDG Rev 29MAY2025.</Para>
<?FTID-rev start?>
<?FTID-rev end?>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>This MEL is produced in frame maker format and can be published in PDF and in electronic format for electronic consultation on EFB</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
